<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,minimum-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no">
    <title>岩崎学園入学式2019</title>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "top" %>
</head>
<body>
    <header id="header_wrap">
        <div class="border_wrapper">
            <div class="border_top border_animation"></div>
            <div class="border_radius_top"></div>
            <div class="scroll_text">scroll</div>
        </div>
        <div class="info_container">
            <figure>
                <%= image_tag "logo.png" %>
            </figure>
            <div class="info">
                <%= image_tag "iwasaki_logo.svg", :class => "main_logo" %>                                        
                <button class="app_button"><a href="http://iwasaki2019.com:3000/user/show">WEBアプリを起動 ></a></button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div id="mask">
            <section>
                <div class="info_img">
                    <%= image_tag "hello_isc.png" %>
                </div>
                <p class="attention">
                    <span>
                        新入生の皆さん<br>
                        ご入学おめでとうございます!<br>
                    </span>
                    <span class="attention_section">
                        私たち情報科学専門は<br>
                        <span class="strong">【 IT × アイドル 】</span><br>
                        をテーマにパフォーマンスを披露します。<br>
                    </span>
                    <span>
                        こちらではアイドルライブを盛り上げる<br>
                        WEBアプリの使い方をご説明します。<br>
                    </span>
                </p>
                <button class="start_button">
                    <div>
                        <%= image_tag "button_icon.png" %>
                        <span>起動</span>
                    </div>
                </button>
                <div class="next_border_wrap">
                    <div class="border_top next_border"></div>
                    <div class="border_radius_top"></div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section>
            <ul id="app_info_container">
                <li>
                    <figure class="description">
                        <%= image_tag "app_image_1.gif", :class => "app_main_image" %>
                    </figure>
                    <h3 class="number_label"><div>1</div></h3>
                    <p class="main_text">
                        WEBアプリに<br>
                        アクセス
                    </p>
                    <div class="next_border_wrap next-margin-top">
                        <div class="border_top next_border"></div>
                        <div class="border_radius_top"></div>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <figure class="description">
                        <%= image_tag "app_image_2.gif", :class => "app_main_image" %>
                    </figure>
                    <%= image_tag "app_image_3.png", :class => "cover_app_image" %>
                    <h3 class="number_label"><div>2</div></h3>
                    <p class="main_text">
                        スマホを振ると<br>
                        アイドルたちに「いいね！」を<br>
                        送信することができます
                    </p>
                    <div class="next_border_wrap next-margin-top">
                        <div class="border_top next_border"></div>
                        <div class="border_radius_top"></div>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <figure class="app_image_wrapper">
                        <%= image_tag "app_image_3_1.png", :class => "app_image" %>
                        <%= image_tag "app_image_3_2.png", :class => "app_image" %>
                        <%= image_tag "app_image_3_3.png", :class => "app_image" %>
                    </figure>
                    <h3 class="number_label"><div>3</div></h3>
                    <p class="main_text">
                        真ん中のハートをタップすると<br>
                        スマホライトの色が変わる！<br>
                        推しの色で応援しよう
                    </p>
                </li>
            </ul>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <div class="footer_mask">
            <div class="footer_wrapper">
                <div id="footer_logo_container">
                    <%= image_tag "logo.png", :class => "footer_image" %>
                    <div id="footer_top">
                        <%= image_tag "iwasaki_logo.svg", :class => "main_logo" %>                        
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="day">4.6 Sat.</p>
                <small>
                    <span>CAST</span>／さきぴ こっとん はるる みぽりん づっき ゆうたん　<span>開発</span>／Make IT　<span>テスト協力</span>／IPFactory
                </small>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>